#: data/campaigns/Two_Brothers/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:465
#: data/campaigns/Two_Brothers/scenarios/03_Guarded_Castle.cfg:581
msgid "Um, yes. Fine. You can go."
msgstr "Uhm, ja. Gut. Ihr könnt gehen."

